      <li>Documentation tool to create a class inventory in HTML format
        from an Eiffel source tree.</li>
      <li>A web publishing application configured by an XML script to
        create multiple views of HTML documents created in the
        Thunderbird
        email client HTML editor.</li>
      <li>An application to perform off-site archiving of project files
        featuring:</li>
      <ul>
        <li>Backups scripted with XML.</li>
        <li>File filtering and wildcards.</li>
        <li>Optional cyclical versioning upto a maximum version.</li>
        <li>Optional gpg encryption for selected directories.</li>
        <li>Archive compression.</li>
        <li>Offsite transfer of all archives via ftp.</li>
      </ul>
